keyboards.name: Champ Membrane Keyboard
keyboards.description: The Champ is a highly user-friendly and compatible keyboard. Its size and weight give a smooth handling and typing experience. And the ergonomic design brings comfort while typing, thus enabling easy and effortless keystrokes.

keyboards.name: Champ BK372 Multi device wireless keyboard
keyboards.description: With the Champ BK372, you get a slim, ergonomic, lightweight Bluetooth keyboard that supports multiple devices. The easy-switch button makes it possible to connect with up to three Android, Windows, or Mac OS devices at once. The long-lasting battery ensures uninterrupted usage, and the integrated cradle holds smartphones or tablets for better typing and viewing angles.
